              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4465736372697074696f6e23232344415441232323">The Rosarius generates an energy field that provides the Chaplain with a 4+ Invulnerable Save. This may be taken instead of the Chaplain&apos;s normal Armour Save.</characteristic>
